			span(data-i18n='professional-serious-weapon') Serious Weapons
		|  
		i
			| &nbsp;(
			span(data-i18n='pick-one') pick one
			| )
		| :
	.sheet-move.sheet-Setting-Default
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Professional_seriousgearchoice1')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='professional-gear3') Assault rifle (3 harm, far, area, loud, reload)
	.sheet-move.sheet-Setting-Default
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Professional_seriousgearchoice2')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='professional-gear4') Grenade launcher (4 harm, far, area, messy, loud, reload)
