		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Professional_seriousgearchoice3')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='professional-gear5') Sniper rifle (4 harm, far)
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Professional_seriousgearchoice4')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='professional-gear6') Grenades (4 harm, close, area, messy, loud)
	.sheet-move.sheet-Setting-Default
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Professional_seriousgearchoice5')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='professional-gear7') Submachine gun (3 harm, close, area, loud, reload)
